<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">This Act may be cited as the “Agricultural Marketing Agreement Act of 1937”.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idee57a1b8-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/act/1937-06-03/ch296/s6">June 3, 1937, ch. 296, § 6</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/50/249">50 Stat. 249</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
