<note style="-uslm-lc:I75" topic="referencesInText" id="idee57a1bb-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">
<heading class="centered smallCaps">References in Text</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">This Act, referred to in text, is <ref href="/us/act/1937-06-03/ch296">act June 3, 1937, ch. 296</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/50/246">50 Stat. 246</ref>, which among other things enacted this chapter. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Tables.</p>
